本訊息模板為說明馬種資料，格式沿自英文維基相同名稱的模板。

== 用法 ==
可以將下列空白模板複製到條目中，然後填入所需資料即可：
<pre style="overflow: auto;">
<!-- Begin Infobox horse breed. The text of the article should go AFTER this section. -->
{{Infobox horse breed
| name            = <!-- if omitted, defaults to article title -->
| image           = <!-- just the image file name, such as image.jpg -->
| image_caption   = 
| image_alt       = <!-- wiki-markup won't work here -->
| features        = 
| altname         = <!-- for multiple values, please use {{ubl| ... | ... }} instead of <br> -->
| nickname        = <!-- for multiple values, please use {{ubl| ... | ... }} instead of <br> -->
| country         = <!-- use name of country or region of origin that was in use at that time -->
| group1          = 
| std1            = 
| group2          = 
| std2            = 
| group3          = 
| std3            = 
| group4          = 
| std4            = 
| group5          = 
| std5            = 
| group6          = 
| std6            = 
| status          = [not recognized|extinct]
| note            = 
}}
<!-- End Infobox horse info. Article begins here -->
</pre>

